    <p>
        <b>
            <a href="#close" class="hide">
                [x] click to close
            </a>
        </b>
    </p>
    <div id="map_vothC89" style="width: 250px; height: 250px;"></div>
                        <p class="placename">
                Plaszow<br /><span class="alt">(Krakw-Plaszw)</span>
            </p>
                            <p class="subcamp_of">
                <strong>Subcamp of: </strong>
                Majdanek
            </p>
                            <p class="municipality">
                <strong>Location:</strong>
                Krak&#195;w, Poland<br />
                            </p>
                            <div>
                This slave labor camp near Krak&#195;w was headed by Amon Goeth, a psychopathic killer. Of some 150,000 Jews who passed through its gates, about 80,000 perished.
            </div>
