    </p>
    <div id="map_vothC143" style="width: 250px; height: 250px;"></div>
                        <p class="placename">
                Radom Ghetto
            </p>
                            <p class="subcamp_of">
                <strong>Subcamp of: </strong>
                Majdanek
            </p>
                            <p class="municipality">
                <strong>Location:</strong>
                Radom, Poland<br />
                            </p>
                            <div>
                Radom had a pre-war population of approximately 25,000 Jews. The ghetto was created in March 1941. Most residents were deported to Auschwitz or Treblinka in 1942.
            </div>
                            <style type="text/css">
.olLayerDiv{
