            </a>
        </b>
    </p>
    <div id="map_vothC144" style="width: 250px; height: 250px;"></div>
                        <p class="placename">
                Kranik
            </p>
                            <p class="subcamp_of">
                <strong>Subcamp of: </strong>
                Majdanek
            </p>
                            <p class="municipality">
                <strong>Location:</strong>
                Kranik, Poland<br />
                            </p>
                            <div>
                This labor camp was liberated in July 1944. Most of the Jews of the camp though went to Majdanek in March 1944. Only 300 were saved.
            </div>
